alias.cw: .msg $aircraft Bonjour! You will enter my airspace shortly. Please contact me on $freq when $1.
alias.cp: .msg $aircraft Bonjour! You will enter my airspace shortly. Please contact me on $freq when passing $uc($1).
alias.cwr: .msg $aircraft Bonjour! $radioname is providing top-down service for $dep. Please contact me on $freq when you are ready.
alias.ci: .msg $aircraft NO MOVEMENT without permission, please! $radioname is providing top-down service for $dep. HOLD POSITION and contact me IMMEDIATELY on $freq!
alias.v?: Are you able to receive voice?
alias.noatc: You are leaving my airspace, no further ATC service available, radar service terminated. Monitor UNICOM on 122.800 and have a good flight, au revoir!
alias.noatcb: $radioname is closing, no further ATC service available, radar service terminated. Monitor UNICOM on 122.800 and have a good flight, au revoir!
alias.noatcc: $radioname is closing, for further ATC service contact $radioname($1) $freq($1), au revoir!
alias.noatco: You are outside of my airspace, continue own discretion and monitor UNICOM on 122.800, au revoir!
alias.blt: Please use UNICOM 122.800 for blind transmissions. Thank you.
alias.cdm: .msg $aircraft CDM in use, please confirm your TBOT at cdm.vatsim.fr as requested in the ATIS (mandatory for departure)
alias.exp: .msg $aircraft Your filed EOBT has expired, please confirm your new TOBT at cdm.vatsim.fr as requested in the ATIS (mandatory for departure)
alias.rrc: Clearance available, report ready to copy.
alias.cl: Runway $deprwy, cleared to $arr via $sid departure, climb to $temp , squawk $squawk.
alias.clf: Piste $deprwy, mise en route approuve vers $arr, depart $sid, montez $temp, transpondeur $squawk.
alias.clv: Runway $deprwy, cleared to $arr via vectored departure. After departure climb to $temp and maintain runway heading, squawk $squawk.
alias.clvf: Piste $deprwy, mise en route approuve vers $arr, depart omnidirectionnel. Montez $temp dans l'axe, transpondeur $squawk.
alias.sid?: Are you able to fly the $sid departure?
alias.spaf: Mise en route et repoussage approuve.
alias.thp: Taxi to holding point runway $deprwy via $1.
alias.thpf: Roulez au point d'attente piste $deprwy via $1.
alias.tihp: Taxi to intermediate holding position $1 (runway $deprwy) via $2.
alias.ttc: Taxi to a parking position of your choice.
alias.ths: Taxi via $1, hold short of runway $2.
alias.lubl: Behind landing $1, line up runway $deprwy and wait behind.
alias.lubd: Behind departing $1, line up runway $deprwy and wait behind.
alias.rfid: Are you ready for immediate departure?
alias.afid: Are you able for departure from intersection $1?
alias.ctoi: Wind $winds($dep), runway $deprwy, intersection $1, cleared for take-off.
alias.cito: Wind $winds($dep), runway $deprwy, cleared for immediate take-off.
alias.toc: Hold position, CANCEL take-off, I say again, CANCEL take-off.
alias.ron: Resume own navigation direct $uc($1), magnetic track $bear($1) distance $dist($1) miles.
alias.wrdr: When ready, descend to FL $1 to reach level at $2.
alias.cas: Check altimeter setting and confirm level. You are indicating $calt.
alias.sas: Set altimeter to standard pressure (1013 hPa or 2992 inHg).
alias.le: Currently only EVEN levels available. Do you prefer FL $1 or FL $2?
alias.lo: Currently only ODD levels available. Do you prefer FL $1 or FL $2?
alias.et: Expect RNAV transition for $1 approach runway $arrrwy.
alias.ils: Cleared ILS approach runway $arrrwy. Report established.
alias.autoclearedils: Cleared ILS approach runway $1. Report established.
alias.rnav: Cleared RNAV approach runway $arrrwy. Report established.
alias.vor: Cleared VOR/DME approach runway $arrrwy. Report established.
alias.ndb: Cleared NDB approach runway $arrrwy. Report established.
alias.vi: Cleared Visual approach runway $arrrwy. Report runway in sight.
alias.autoclearedvisual: Cleared Visual approach runway $1. Report runway in sight.
alias.llc: Continue approach, expect late landing clearance, wind $winds($arr).
alias.mcr: Reduce to minimum clean speed and report.
alias.hor: Hold at $1, inbound track $2, right hand pattern.
alias.hol: Hold at $1, inbound track $2, left hand pattern.
alias.ctg: Wind $winds($arr), runway $arrrwy, cleared touch and go.
alias.csg: Wind $winds($arr), runway $arrrwy, cleared for stop and go.
alias.avr: After landing vacate to the RIGHT.
alias.avl: After landing vacate to the LEFT.
alias.bye: Thanks for coming to $arr, good bye and see you next time.
alias.csr: .msg $aircraft At the moment, your call sign is not listed in our database. Please register your airline on gng.aero-nav.com/AERONAV/icao_request_airlines. If you continue to fly in our region, your call sign may be included in our controller files.
alias.csv: .msg $aircraft At the moment, your call sign is not listed in our database. Please register your VA on gng.aero-nav.com/AERONAV/icao_request_vairlines. If you continue to fly in our region, your call sign may be included in our controller files.
